{"tid":1474186,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"憂解放軍對香港出手 紐西蘭政府擬定撤僑計畫","createTime":"2019-08-15T05:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T05:55:50.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b8c5bee7719c0cd5e0f7e699c20d39d9038efe2b","tid":1474186,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:35:51.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕香港反送中活動持續延燒，傳出中國當局不滿局勢惡化，已陳兵邊境伺機而動，美國總統川普昨也在推特上爆料，中國政府「正調動部隊到香港邊境」，紐西蘭政府已著手制定撤僑計畫，以便在必要時撤離留港紐西蘭僑民。<br />\n<br />\n據紐西蘭媒體龍頭《Newstalk ZB》報導，該媒體政治編輯索珀（Barry Soper）表示，中國當局準軍事部隊陳兵香港邊境僅30公里，已引發外界疑慮，加上香港特首林鄭月娥揚言，若持續縱容「暴力」行為，將把香港推向一條不歸路。<br />\n<br />\n隨著香港局勢恐進一步惡化，紐西蘭外交和貿易部（MFAT）已著手製定計劃，以便在必要時撤離滯留香港的紐西蘭僑民；報導指出，香港約有1萬名紐西蘭僑民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2885010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2885010&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdq2paxXJRTFpYESBXKIXFX0%3D&h=89b6093f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2885010&h=25f0e592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2885010</a>"},{"pid":"ef0d19ed38c2a741cb6bba5e40816f85e285c958","tid":1474186,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:43:31.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n可以賽後檢討，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It is now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YvdK1E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YvdK1E.jpg&h=e1c38679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D83Sf8j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD83Sf8j.jpg&h=da01072f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JSeBHOk.jpg\" da